"  <div class=\"headingAnchor\" id=\"references\">",
"   <h1>",
"    REFERENCES",
"   </h1>",
"   <ol id=\"reference\">",
"    <li>",
"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?33/35/34359/abstract/1\">",
"      Boyer TD. Transjugular intrahepatic portosystemic shunt: current status. Gastroenterology 2003; 124:1700.",
